sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Gateway
    participant PostService as Social Post Service
    participant PostWorker as Social Post Worker
    participant PublishWorker as Social Publish Worker
    participant PlatformAdapter as Social Platform Adapter
    participant ExternalAPI as Facebook / LinkedIn API

    User->>Gateway: POST /social/posts {page_id, provider, message}
    Gateway->>PostService: Forward Request
    PostService->>PostService: Check XLEN jobs:social-post <= 10000
    PostService->>Gateway: Return {"status": "enqueued", "job_id": "..."}
    Gateway->>User: Return {"status": "enqueued", "job_id": "..."}

    PostService->>PostWorker: XADD jobs:social-post

    PostWorker->>PostWorker: Check idempotency & StateManager.get_last_step()
    PostWorker->>PostWorker: Save post in DB -> StateManager.save_step("db_stored")
    PostWorker->>PublishWorker: XADD jobs:social-publish {type: "publish_post"}
    PostWorker->>PostWorker: XACK & XDEL jobs:social-post

    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: Check idempotency & StateManager.get_last_step()
    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: Fetch access token -> StateManager.save_step("token_retrieved")
    PublishWorker->>PlatformAdapter: publish(page_id, message, token)
    PlatformAdapter->>ExternalAPI: HTTP POST /v19.0/{page_id}/feed
    ExternalAPI-->>PlatformAdapter: Return {id: "post_12345"}
    PlatformAdapter-->>PublishWorker: Return "post_12345"

    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: StateManager.save_step("completed")
    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: SET job_state:{id} "completed"
    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: SET job_result:{id} "post_12345"
    PublishWorker->>PublishWorker: XACK & XDEL jobs:social-publish
